               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18410920-name-349" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18410920-name-349" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18410920-name-349" type="surname" value="DENT"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18410920-name-349" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM DENT</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a butcher, and live in Blackman-street, Clare-market. On Saturday night, the 11th of September, about eight o'clock in the evening, I saw the prisoner standing close by my shop—another boy took a shoulder of mutton off the hook, and the prisoner received it—the other boy got off—the prisoner ran down Blackman-street—I pursued and took him—he dropped the mutton—I made him take it up again, and bring it back to my shop.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18410920-name-350" type="witnessName">
