                        <interp inst="t18410920-name-350" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE WILKIN</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a policeman. I took the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I was in a mob; a young man turned round and threw the mutton right in my breast; I stood looking at it, and the man came and took me.</p>
